{"tid":1273061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一光復立法會文宣","createTime":"2019-07-01T13:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T09:02:22.000Z","uid":269054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7ca137fa2e7d763153919cf273db1a95517750","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"衝入立法會已成事實，<br />\n而家可以做既就要說服和理非<br />\n聽到好多中產唔支持衝擊立法會<br />\n希望多d人幫手 喧傳點解要衝<br />\n制造一個支持義士既 輿論風向<br />\n<br />\n1. Share成功例子 太陽花學運<br />\n2. Share 支持既文章"},{"pid":"0d8c5ee1ccad98e22b2e4d89fa61351146cb4079","tid":1273061,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，屌嗰啲當然90%都係五毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，呢個就係拉籠一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟，共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持清醒，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易上五毛當</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"56dfd80f9bf0a27cca6f777880d8049f9ddb0215","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc7ca137fa2e7d763153919cf273db1a95517750","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"衝入立法會已成事實，<br />\n而家可以做既就要說服和理非<br />\n聽到好多中產唔支持衝擊立法會<br />\n希望多d人幫手 喧傳點解要衝<br />\n制造一個支持義士既 輿論風向<br />\n<br />\n1. Share成功例子 太陽花學運<br />\n2. Share 支持既文章"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxCmeRR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxCmeRR.png&h=66813373&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e1c122dde3941cbf80d3d60d0a7062324d1aab9","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56dfd80f9bf0a27cca6f777880d8049f9ddb0215","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc7ca137fa2e7d763153919cf273db1a95517750","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"衝入立法會已成事實，<br />\n而家可以做既就要說服和理非<br />\n聽到好多中產唔支持衝擊立法會<br />\n希望多d人幫手 喧傳點解要衝<br />\n制造一個支持義士既 輿論風向<br />\n<br />\n1. Share成功例子 太陽花學運<br />\n2. Share 支持既文章"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxCmeRR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxCmeRR.png&h=66813373&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/825244965/posts/10158784027684966?s=1257948478&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F825244965%2Fposts%2F10158784027684966%3Fs%3D1257948478%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=80b16201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/825244965/posts/10158784027684966?s=1257948478&amp;sfns=xmo</a><br />\n<br />\n轉載三段字，該能很好說明現在的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n//有人說：「你哋衝入去，係會當成暴動，要坐十年㗎！入面仲要準備晒槍等你哋㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n有人回答：「預咗啦！已經有三個人死咗啦！我哋預咗啦！」//<br />\n<br />\n//睇直播見到幾個議員頂住㗎車唔畀人撞入去，啲𡃁仔講「你畀我哋撞入去啦！我預咗比人拉㗎啦！你仲想我哋等幾耐呀？仲有乜嘢方法呀」//<br />\n<br />\n//有說:<br />\n在現場的社工朋友透露，他們不是鬼，而係死士，有十幾人，預了無咗條命😥。另一朋友也說，現場青少年告昨晚煲底開會，有九人舉手做死士<br />\n所以佢哋係想自殺，不過用另一方式。😭😭😭//<br />\n<br />\n有識之士們，指責在極悲極憤下想做點甚麼的人，是沒有意思的。<br />\n<br />\n這個麻木不仁的嗜血政權，已經奪走了至少三條性命了。面對這樣的悲憤，他們已經是接近在求死的階段了。<br />\n<br />\n你若認為你自己是有識之士，去用盡一切方法告訴今早在飲血的惡魔、嗜血的狂徒吧，盡你所能，勸他們、叫他們、逼他們收手吧。<br />\n<br />\n很多很多的性命，已經危在旦夕了，拜托你們，收口吧。<br />\n<br />\n去做點甚麼吧。"},{"pid":"7cb99390d96a5fd7f6918d92d9ef9afea4ecc395","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc7ca137fa2e7d763153919cf273db1a95517750","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"衝入立法會已成事實，<br />\n而家可以做既就要說服和理非<br />\n聽到好多中產唔支持衝擊立法會<br />\n希望多d人幫手 喧傳點解要衝<br />\n制造一個支持義士既 輿論風向<br />\n<br />\n1. Share成功例子 太陽花學運<br />\n2. Share 支持既文章"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"青年新政就衝擊立法會事件之聲明<br />\n<br />\n在主權移交後的22年，今年6月香港迎來最壞的時刻，送中條例令香港的法治危在旦夕，香港人群起反抗，可是-<br />\n<br />\n一百萬人遊行，政府絲毫沒有退讓；<br />\n<br />\n二百萬人遊行，政府仍然沒有回應訴求；<br />\n<br />\n全球登報反送中, G20各國政要關注, 政府繼續裝聾作啞；<br />\n<br />\n三位義士以死控訴，冷血無情的政府依舊歌舞昇平, 閉門升旗冷待香港人的訴求；<br />\n<br />\n香港人還可以怎樣做？所以，有一群義人決定行動升級，迫使777作出回應。 雖然立法會今天未有會議，他們仍然決定對立法會作出衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n被保皇黨控制、沒有民意授權的立法會從來只是為政權保駕護航的橡皮圖章，他們代表不了香港人、保護不了香港人、他們甚至不能稱為香港人，他們只是一群眷戀權位的賣港賊！<br />\n<br />\n衝擊立法會雖然激進, 但絕對是天經地義、合情合理。 義人深知一旦被捕有可能面對長年監禁，亦明瞭在衝擊中可能會受傷、甚至失去性命。 但在絕望的困局中，他們決定視死如歸, 犧牲自己保護香港，繼承三位戰友的遺志。<br />\n<br />\n鐵籠車再堅硬、鐵枝再尖銳、也抵不上無恥港共政權對香港人的壓迫。 有人選擇以死控訴，有人選擇衝擊極權象徵立法會以明志，這都是香港人在殺人政權高壓下作出的最後吶喊和反抗。 社會的不安寧，從來只有施加壓迫的一方才有能力制止。 林鄭月娥，你已經不能再迴避問題，再多的空言虛語不會軟化到香港人的決心，只有正面回應香港人的四大訴求，並使施暴的黑警付出代價，才可避免成為人類文明的公敵。<br />\n<br />\n#FreeHK"},{"pid":"9af043f23c7b75038b751d1038d648edaa3455c3","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/91460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F91460&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=64ab4892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/91460</a><br />\n<br />\n【判決全文】太陽花佔領立院二審再判無罪，因「屬最後必要手段」"},{"pid":"42ac47caf860219df297d16d16143428f64f3238","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"其中《衛報》報道，記者在立法會外訪問了以黑色圍巾蒙頭的32歲示威者Alan，他道出部分示威者衝擊立法會的原因，「數以百萬人出來示威，但政府無視我們的訴求，今次(衝擊)是為了向政府進一步施壓。我們不知道這有沒有用，只希望另覓方法，令政府認真看待我們。如果這(衝擊)沒有用，我們也沒甚麼可輸。」他並反問︰「有甚麼渠道能令林鄭月娥聆聽我們？我們只想為所爭取的展示決心，不惜任何代價！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E8%A1%9B%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%8B%E8%A8%AA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%EF%B8%B0-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9F-178585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25A1%259D%25E6%2593%258A%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%2591%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E3%2580%258B%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25EF%25B8%25B0-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B3%2595%25EF%25BC%259F-178585&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=83b90ac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E8%A1%9B%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%8B%E8%A8%AA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%EF%B8%B0-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9F-178585</a>"},{"pid":"0f9c2936ffa5ac89cf319e098216be21a4b2725c","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AfnKWn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AfnKWn.png&h=0e24479d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dba0aae3d53d26ba80eb1ea8e74c542071c6ca18","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:00:08.000Z","msg":"請問又幾多件暴政的事讓你產生的憤怒比爆玻璃大？<br />\n玻璃最多影響一星期，自由行、領匯呢d影響左民生十幾年。換玻璃當你1萬，高鐵超資多過200億。<br />\n暴力爆玻璃係唔啱，但只罵暴力爆玻璃而不罵暴力通過法案的似乎不太公平。<br />\n<br />\n2003，被隱瞞的沙士。<br />\n2003，基本法二十三條。<br />\n2004，自由行<br />\n2005，領匯上市<br />\n2007，皇后碼頭事件。<br />\n2010，高鐵撥款，由669億超支至900億元<br />\n2012，國民洗腦科。<br />\n2013，香港電視攞唔到牌照。<br />\n2014，版權修訂條例草案（網絡廿三條）。<br />\n2014，「袋住先」篩選普選。<br />\n2014，新界東北撥款，暫時335億<br />\n2015，啟晴邨鉛水事件。<br />\n2015，銅鑼灣書局事件。<br />\n2015，三跑填海，由原本550億超支到預計1415億元，仍未完成<br />\n2016，DQ議員。<br />\n2016，港珠澳大橋撥款，由原本762億超支到1177億元<br />\n2017，國歌法<br />\n2018，割地兩檢。<br />\n2018，飛沙風中線。<br />\n2018，山竹「安全渡過」論。<br />\n2018，馬凱不獲簽證。<br />\n2018，被隱瞞非洲豬瘟疫情<br />\n2019，修訂逃犯條例 及 警察使用過度武力。<br />\n2019，中環海濱送中。"},{"pid":"438e7f436a52646173951d439c7ae56267703545","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:06:45.000Z","msg":"【 學下官腔】如何應對短期内排山倒海的「嚴厲譴責示威人士使用暴力」？ 給香港的七點回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1274862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1274862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9bdcee931f35d4ea3a31fedbdc546bede6376ef","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:38:10.000Z","msg":"有未訓的文宣組可以來討論怎樣拆今日事故？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1274289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1274289</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8f4adc7808e813dc632b851ce39f589c37963ec","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:30:36.000Z","msg":"【緊急預警】文宣戰線請宜家開始準備！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4dea38f8731fc0a0873e43745d93b20335120660","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:38:30.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 7.1 發生嘅唔係暴力行為 - 係 官逼民反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1aad8fdfcdd2de10aeb93350fc5be753ebd1002","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"[同我推撚爆佢] 他們不是在衝擊。他們在自殺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b856c3aa2b71680d9e0805d0ea416ebb90b8641","tid":1273061,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"1500學生癱瘓州議會大廈 抗議警察槍殺非裔青少年<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/13833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F13833&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=3db17c93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/13833</a>"}]}